721
00:36:18,159 --> 00:36:19,239
Sama-sama.

722
00:36:38,000 --> 00:36:38,919
Fanlu.

723
00:36:39,879 --> 00:36:41,399
Kalau awak benar-benar ditimpa malang,

724
