726
00:36:49,520 --> 00:36:50,760
Bukankah begitu?

727
00:36:52,040 --> 00:36:53,479
Kenapa awak kata begitu?

728
00:36:54,280 --> 00:36:55,199
Fanlu.

729
00:36:56,520 --> 00:36:58,399
